              "item_id": "item-0013",
              "item_type": "solution",
              "title": "解** 由 $AB = AC$ 得 $\\angle ABC = \\angle ACB$。由 $BD = BC$ 得 $\\angle BDC = \\angle C$。从而 $\\angle ABD = \\angle ABC - \\angle DBC = \\angle ACB - \\angle BDC = \\angle DBC$。",
              "text": "解** 由 $AB = AC$ 得 $\\angle ABC = \\angle ACB$。由 $BD = BC$ 得 $\\angle BDC = \\angle C$。从而 $\\angle ABD = \\angle ABC - \\angle DBC = \\angle ACB - \\angle BDC = \\angle DBC$。",
